<br>
&quot;People can hide behind anonymity and a computer screen there is very little responsibility involved.&quot; <br>
-  This has always been true.  I won't go into the large area of internet use and abuse; we all know the internet's merits and its problems.<br>
<br>
&quot;Just because pedophiles, criminals, terrorists, cyber-stalkers, rapists (the list goes on) exist, doesn't mean they should.&quot;  <br>
